citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:00am on
February 7, 2023. The licensee was contacted via telephone and informed the inspectors that they were out of state and
another responsible adult was unavailable to conduct the inspection.
Additional Inspectors:
KATHARINE FRANK, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
